                    </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span class="tech-tag">
                        <img src="img/rabbitmq.png" style="margin-top: -10px;"/>
                        <b>RabbitMQ</b>
                    </span>
                    <span class="tech-tag">
                        <b>- MassTransit</b>
                    </span>
